       either ssssyyyysssstttteeeemmmm....mmmmwwwwmmmmrrrrcccc (to make system-wide changes) or ....mmmmwwwwmmmmrrrrcccc
       (to make changes to the local environment).  The easiest way
       is to change the default bindings or to insert extra lines
       in the DefaultKeyBindings section.

